defmodule Solution do
  @spec beautiful_indices(s :: String.t, a :: String.t, b :: String.t, k :: integer) :: [integer]
  def beautiful_indices(s, a, b, k) do
    a_indices = find_indices(s, a)
    b_indices = find_indices(s, b)

    Enum.filter(a_indices, fn i ->
      Enum.any?(b_indices, fn j -> abs(j - i) <= k end)
    end)
  end

  defp find_indices(s, sub) do
    for i <- 0..(String.length(s) - String.length(sub)),
        String.slice(s, i, String.length(sub)) == sub,
        do: i
  end
end
